<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa" crossorigin="anonymous" defer></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="itempage.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">

    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/b2cb25ccdb.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>RealBay</title>
</head>
<body id="body">
    <div class="cnavbar">
      <button id="logobtn" type="button" name="button">
        <img class="navbarLogo" src="images/Logo.png" alt="Realbay-Logo">
      </button>
        <button class="cbtn-tags cbtn">Tags</button>

        <form class="searchbarForm" action="/" method="post">
            <input class="searchbar" type="text" name="searchInput">
            <button class="cbtn" type="submit">Search</button>
        </form>

        <button class="cbtn cbtn-profile"><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i></button>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="images/cat.png" class="article-img-lg" alt="article-img">
        <div class="article-txt">
            <h1 >Süße Katze</h1>
            <p class="describtion-sm">
                Will meine Katze verkaufen, kotzt zu viel.
            </p>
            <p class="describtion-lg">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Itaque, eligendi perspiciatis quae consequuntur excepturi tempore exercitationem natus, aliquam hic voluptates alias. Rem distinctio assumenda corrupti, explicabo illo sed optio! Earum.
            </p>
            <hr>
            <h2>Produktinormationen</h2>
            <table class="article-info">
                <tr>
                    <td>Gewicht</td>
                    <td>20kg</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Größe</td>
                    <td>80cm*10cm*20cm</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Alter</td>
                    <td>12 Jahre</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="merchant container">
        <button class="merchant-btn" ></button>
        <div style="margin: 20px 0 0 20px">
            <h2>Merchant</h2>
            <p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <i class="fa-brands fa-1x fa-twitter responsive-icon icon"></i>
        <i class="fa-brands fa-1x fa-instagram responsive-icon icon"></i>
        <i class="fa-brands fa-1x fa-facebook-f responsive-icon icon"></i>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-1x fa-envelope responsive-icon icon"></i>
        <p>© Copyright</p>
    </footer>
    <script  src ="event-handler.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

</body>
</html>
